Description:
ONE BEDDER PLUS STUDY
This 6th floor 1 bedroom (plus study) apartment at VICTORIA POINT is sure to impress even the most discerning buyers. Moments from the heart of the Melbournes CBD, enjoy a relaxed harbour-side lifestyle with waterfront restaurants, convenient supermarket shopping and free CBD trams all on your doorstep.
Full sized kitchen with island bench, stone counter tops and stainless steel appliances opens onto a huge open plan living space with plenty of room for dining, living and study. Full length windows/sliding doors captures a truly unique view back out over the water.
Double bedroom with full length mirrored robes and also sharing a waterfront view, it boasts brilliant natural light and practical storage solutions. Functional central bathroom with stone benches, walk in shower and euro laundry.
Rounding out this fabulous opportunity is secure undercover parking plus a storage cage, a concealed laundry, ducted heating and cooling, roller blinds, on-site building manager and concierge, secure swipe/intercom entry, and exclusive access to the building's facilities including a fully equipped gym
Insights: 604/100 Harbour Esplanade, Docklands VIC 3008 was last sold in 2019 and 141 other 1 bedroom unit in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
Loft Style Luxury At Its Best
If you're after a unique three level loft style home then this is the apartment for you! The Elm & Stone is the latest project by award-winning developer MAB Corporation. This is one of the best boutique developments around that consists of only 144 apartments. Perfect for any astute owner-occupier's or savvy investors that want quality and exclusivity!
This stunning two bedroom, two bathroom loft is located on the 5th floor with direct north facing views, a very spacious floor plan, sophisticated DKO designed interiors, grey wash oak timber flooring, SMEG appliances,stone bench-tops, a stunning tiled splash-back, integrated dishwasher, built-in robes, a European laundry, and a secured car park. Two of the most unique features that you will not find in any other building in Docklands is one of a kind stunning high ceilings and the top floor loft that can double as a second living room, a home office or a guest room.
Exclusive Elm & Stone amenities include a resident's gym, lap-pool, library, and a lush central garden. Conveniently located within the free city tram zone, Elm & Stone is just minutes to Melbourne's CBD, District Docklands Shopping Centre and stunning water-frontage.

Description:
Substance, Style & an Iconic Collins Street Address
Striking an ideal balance of substance and style, this wonderful apartment provides a versatile floorplan designed for flexible living. An apartment well suited to first homebuyers, inner-city professionals and investors alike.
Upon entry, you're welcomed by open plan living and dining areas with floor to ceiling windows. A stunning kitchen with timber style finishes, quality appliances and smart storage is thoroughly gourmet, whilst a purpose built study desk is an inspired feature. Master bedroom has generous built in robes, and together with the second bedroom is full of natural light. The bathroom is beautifully modern. Bonus features include reverse cycle heating/cooling, European laundry and security intercom.
The sought-after Collins Street address steps up the convenience: moments from the central business district, the city's freeway network, whilst free trams and Woolworths are ideally located at your door. Docklands' waterfront, green space, restaurants, cafes and shopping provide the perfect balance of nature and accessibility.
868 Collins Street features everything you'd expect from luxury inner-city living: an indoor heated pool & spa, residents' library, state of the art gymnasium and business lounge.

Northern sun filled one bedroom retreat
With a northern orientation, promising a stunning opportunity for first home buyers and savvy investors alike, this sizable light-filled opportunity is a Boyd Tower beauty!
Primed for buyers searching for a modern Docklands home in the ever popular NewQuay precinct, this 16th floor residence features bright living and meals, stylish kitchen with stainless steel splashback and quality appliances, balcony with views of the northern mountains and Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, bedroom with dual BIRs, two-way bathroom with laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom entry and storage cage.
Enjoy Boyd Tower facilities including a BBQ area, pool, gym and function room. In close proximity to waterside restaurants including Mama Rumaan, Woolshed, Sir Basil, and Cargo just to name a few, The District Docklands, Marvel Stadium, and the 30, 70, and 86 trams.

Description:
MODERN, CHIC & SLEEK
You are sure to be impressed by this chic 2 bed, 1 bath home in the sought after Quays Complex, ideally located in Newquay, Docklands.
This cool home offers an open plan living zone offering oodles of natural light set off by a wrap around balcony displaying a vista from the north to the east. Stepping onto the huge balcony provides a sensational view from Mt Macedon all the way to CBD. The designer kitchen comprises of stainless steel appliances, dishwasher drawer, and granite bench-tops, with loads of cupboard space and microwave nook.
The master bedroom includes a mirrored built-in robe, and both come with plenty of natural light. The the bathroom is sleek & modern, and has an abundance of cupboard and shelf space.
A Euro-laundry, split system heating/cooling, modern fixtures & fittings, a secure car park, and secure swipe/intercom entry complete this elegant Docklands home.
Typical of modern apartment living, this property comes with a pool, sauna, gym, tennis court, and library for use by all residents. Wonderfully situated close to public transport, and with an array of waterside restaurants and world class shopping on your doorstep, this must see home is also only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.
Don't miss out, book an inspection today.

A Lifestyle or Investment Opportunity at its Best!
Don't miss out on this opportunity to purchase this stylish Dual Key apartment in the well renown Victoria Point! This two in one apartment has access to a spacious one-bedroom apartment as well as stylish studio apartment, each with their own entries. Use them as separate living quarters, perfect for astute investors to capitalise on a double rental return, or even an owner occupier that wants that bit of extra space. They both encompass a modern kitchen with stone bench tops, stainless steel appliances, glass splash back and gas cooking facilities, luxurious separate bathrooms, European laundries, along with separate balconies that capture stunning views of Port Phillip Bay and Melbourne CBD.

Conveniently located within the free city tram zone, you are just minutes to Melbourne's CBD, Southern Cross Station, Marvel Stadium, local schools and universities, cafe's, bars and restaurant, District Docklands Shopping Centre and stunning water-frontage.

Description:
Special Arkley Views of Victoria Harbour **Under Contract**
Ideally located on the fifteenth floor of the masterly designed Arkley building. Sensational harbour views and the renowned Docklands sunsets sweeping across to the Bolte Bridge will delight.
Arkley is located in the heart of New Quay and just a short stroll to District Docklands shopping precinct, waterfront cafes and restaurants, the Melbourne Star, cinema, Marvel Stadium precinct and Free Tram zone to the CBD.
The spacious living and dining area opens to a private balcony with ample room for entertaining, outdoor eating and relaxed waterfront living. A spacious master suite includes a sizeable study area and full ensuite. An impressive second bedroom is serviced by the main bathroom with separate shower and bath. The roomy, modern kitchen provides ample bench and storage space. The apartment features a separate laundry, full air-conditioning to the living and both bedrooms, secure undercover carpark, storage cage at ground level, secure intercom access and residents heated pool, gym and spa.
Be a part of Arkley and the outstanding Docklands lifestyle it is surrounded by. Inspection highly recommended.

Description:
The Quay to Perfect Living!
Positioned on the top floor in the North Tower of the Quays residential complex, this superb two bedroom apartment encompasses a stylish interior with floor-to-ceiling windows allowing for great natural light, not to mention the amazing northerly view aspect.
Features include a quality modern kitchen with Smeg appliances, an open plan living and dining area which has everyday relaxing in mind, a spacious master bedroom with mirrored built in robes, great second bedroom or study, a contemporary bathroom with mosaic tiles, and a well-positioned balcony with stunning city and mountain views!
Luxurious resort-style amenities include swimming pool, spa, gymnasium, tennis courts and rooftop garden. Residents lounge includes a private dining room, cinema, and boardroom facilities.
This property is perfect for any investor or owner-occupier as its situated only moments from excellent public transport links, Melbourne CBD, Marvel Stadium, and various shopping and dining options including Woolshed, Mama Rumaan, and Mill & Bakery with District Docklands Shopping Centre right at your fingertips!

Lifestyle & Location With An Amazing View! ( Open For Inspection on the south entrance which facing the waterfront)
This stylish apartment delivers modern sophistication class, high-end luxury and a convenient waterside location in an iconic newly completed quality development designed by noted architect Koichi Takada.
An opportunity exists to purchase a new luxury apartment in one of Docklands newest Towers so take advantage now.
Surrounded by expansive views over the Docklands through floor-to-ceiling walls of glass that filter in cascades of natural light, the timeless interior showcases a generous living and dining room stepping out to a north-facing balcony with Melbourne City views, an excellent kitchen appointed with Miele appliances and reconstituted bench-tops, master bedroom with luxurious ensuite bathroom, a second bedroom next & centrally located second bathroom. Lucky residents also get to enjoy access to an array of resort-style amenities including a pool, gym and BBQ facilities.
Features: • Generous living and dining room expanding onto a north-facing balcony with Melbourne City views

• Secure basement parking and bike storage
• Split-system air conditioning units
• Carpeted bedrooms
• Double glazed windows, solar gas-boosted hot water, recycled water and LED lighting

Live the dream in Docklands in this premium position within walking distance to public transport, waterfront dining, retail outlets and so much more that makes Melbourne one of the world's most livable cities in the world.

Description:
An Apartment with Winning Views
In one of New Quays' popular Complex's, Harbour One, this is an ideal place to call home.
This 2 bedroom residence offers a spectacular view towards the city skyline, pure amazement in the evenings with mesmerising lights and colours.
Situated on the 19th floor, perfect for either an owner occupier or investor, this abode has recently been repainted and comes fully furnished with brand new furniture and accessories.
When you walk through the front door, the first thing that your eyes will be drawn to is the balcony with its backdrop of views. The waters of the marina then panning towards the buildings of the city providing a perfect balance of elements.
The apartment with an open plan and dining area adjoins the stylish kitchen with integrated stainless steel appliances. The cabinetry, with a white colour scheme, offers clean lines and complements the dark stone bench tops and glass splashback. Gas stove top, electric oven, the dishwashing machine, refrigerator, and microwave provides all that is necessary for a beautiful home cooked meal.
Both bedrooms with mirrored built in robes share the spacious bathroom with above bench vanity and plenty of storage throughout. Incorporated also is a European laundry.

Ducted heating and cooling
Security entrance
Secure remote access car park and storage
Feature of the complex
Onsite manager
Communal library
Gymnasium

Close distance to the CBD, Victoria market and nearby lush parks
Otherwise, hop in your car and journey on the convenient freeways to your desired destinations.
Superb convenient access to the revamped District Docklands Shopping Hub. Popcorn movie nights at the Hoyts cinema, soon to be completed grocery shopping at Woolworths, celebrate with a splendid bottle of wine at Dan Murphy's.
Take your inspection now.

Description:
Dazzling Docklands Indulgence: Executive Sky Home with Uninterrupted Views
Prepare yourself for unmatched luxury, designer detail and sky-high, spectacular views from every room in this free-flowing 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom Marina Tower apartment. Fronted by glass and sensationally set in a coveted corner position on the 37th floor, embrace this thrilling context for year-round entertaining! Head downstairs and explore the Docklands waterfront precinct with premium shopping at The District, the fitness trails of Ron Barassi Senior Park, and the culinary delights of Newquay restaurants.
From the very first step inside, the show-stopping winter garden entry accentuates the wonderful views. Effortlessly attracting natural light, soak up this dazzling aspect in your very own enclosed sunlit space, versatile enough to double as a home office with a view. Venture further inside and discover ultra-spacious open-plan living and dining, and a sleek, high-end Miele kitchen. Framed by rows of floor-to-ceiling glass from top to bottom, immerse yourself in an all-encompassing view sweeping across Victoria Harbour, Bolte Bridge and Port Phillip Bay. Sharing in the vistas, enjoy a pair of generously sized and robed bedrooms, both serviced by sparkling bathrooms.
Special features comprise a concealed laundry, split-system heating and cooling, roller blinds, intercom entry, and secure parking. The world-class Marina Tower facilities include exclusive access to an opulent lounge, library, private business centre, meeting rooms, a cinema, billiard room, an inviting kitchen and dining area, stunning rooftop pool, and a fully equipped gym. Nothing has been left to chance!
Please call Peter Doan on 0402 959 842 for an inspection.

An Array of stunning Docklands highlights awaits
Featuring an abundance of brilliant space, beautiful marina views to the north-east, and the convenience of being in the Yarras Edge precinct which is a coveted place for owner-occupiers to live, this one bedroom residence is an appealing opportunity in the Array complex.
